<b><br>
Oct 31, 2008:<br>
</b>Just thought we'd surprise everyone with some new mp3 tracks! <br>
&quot;<a href="http://hem.sverker.se/%7Edayw/NoWaveDisco-forErikAhlgren1727.mp3">No 
Wave Disco (for Erik Ahlgren 1727)</a>&quot; [DL/Erik Ahlgren] is about a man 
contemporary with Jonas Alstr&ouml;mer (!<a href="www.riksarkivet.se/default.aspx?id=12104">ereh</a> 
dnuof eb nac sciryl). <br>
For a remix, dig &quot;<a href="http://hem.sverker.se/%7Edayw/OcsidEvawOn-7271NerglhaKirerof.mp3">Ocsid 
Evaw On (7271 Nerglha Kire rof)</a>&quot;. The basic track was recorded at Studio 
Gr&ouml;t in Forshaga Oct 12 and completed the 25th at Studio Dayw, Bandhagen. 
<br>
At the same recent Studio Gr&ouml;t session, &quot;<a href="http://hem.sverker.se/%7Edayw/OneForDaddy.mp3">One 
For Daddy</a>&quot; was recorded, performed by David and a very special special 
guest star: Nora, Gr&ouml;t's daughter. A stripped &quot;<a href="http://hem.sverker.se/%7Edayw/OneForDaddy-bagsonlymix.mp3">bags 
only remix</a>&quot; can be found <a href="http://hem.sverker.se/%7Edayw/OneForDaddy-bagsonlymix.mp3">here</a>. 
<br>
Another Studio Gr&ouml;t session from March 24 this year (with David playing guitar), 
coupled with a Studio Dayw session April 6 (with David and Anna playing clarinets), 
yielded two new tracks: &quot;<a href="http://hem.sverker.se/%7Edayw/ANewStatueForANewPark.mp3">A 
New Statue For A New Park</a>&quot; and &quot;<a href="http://hem.sverker.se/%7Edayw/TheRoosterAndTheHen-ClarinetsInLove.mp3">The 
Rooster And The Hen (Clarinets In Love)</a>&quot;. Enjoy! <br>
