July 7, 2007:<br>
</b>Brand new <a href="http://hem.sverker.se/%7Edayw/IWasSoCloseToKissingYouThen.mp3">mp3</a> 
up for downloadin'! <br>
&quot;<a href="http://hem.sverker.se/%7Edayw/IWasSoCloseToKissingYouThen.mp3">I 
Was So Close To Kissing You Then</a>&quot;, written &amp; performed by David (with 
help from Maestro Gr&ouml;t; drum programming assistance &amp; some &quot;bass&quot; 
guitar corrections), recorded over a period of time at Studio Gr&ouml;t [started 
4 aug 2006!] &amp; Studio Dayw, also featuring - and we're very proud to present 
this - a wonderful <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Uilleann_pipes">Uilleann 
pipes</a> solo by the bag pipe maestro <a href="http://www.myspace.com/theliramanexperience">Jan 
&quot;Liraman&quot; Winter</a>. Thanks, Jan! <br>
