<p><b> December 6, 2004:<br>
  </b>New mp3 for Christmas!<br>
  Yes folks, it&#8217;s time to celebrate the holidays (or not) with The Wonder 
  Boys, who - thanks to good ol&#8217; Bjoerne (en f&aring;r tacke) - has a brand 
  new Christmas song available for download here: <a href="http://www.rorschach.tk/dayw/music/The_Day_Before_Christmas.mp3">The 
  Day Before Christmas</a>. Written and performed by Christian G (all instruments 
  etc) and David L (vocals + a bit of additional percussion). Hurry up, tidy up 
  your soul and get this rare track - it might be gone with the Christmas tree!</p>
