<p><b>June 2, 2004:<br>
  </b>In the swedish newspaper <a href="http://www.svd.se/dynamiskt/noje/did_7547401.asp">Svenska 
  Dagbladet</a>, there&#8217;s an article today about the Elvis cover paraphrase 
  coincidence with The Wonder Boys and <a href="http://www.visi.com/fall">The 
  Fall</a> (see also March news below). Read it, with some comments, <a href="TWBElvisFallSvD2June2004.html">here</a>. 
  Written by Cyril Hellman (who also wrote about David and TWB in <a href="http://www.svd.se/dynamiskt/noje/did_5769130.asp">SvD, 
  June 26 2003</a>).<b> </b></p>
